These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: lemonade, soy-milk, water, tea, almond-milk, coffee
6 different pets are kept: ferret, dog, rabbit, turtle, guinea-pig, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 2. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 5. the owner of the rabbit is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 7. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |    3     |  4   |       5       |   6   |
| Beverage   | tea | coffee | soy-milk    | lemonade | water | almond-milk |
| Pet        | dog      | rat  | turtle | ferret | guinea-pig          | rabbit  |

