.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk, fanta, 7up, water, sprite
There are 6 different nationalities: indian, mexican, pakistani, british, polish, australian
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 2. the indian is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 3. the british is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 4. the british is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 5. the polish is on the far right##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is the pakistani##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 8. the australian is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the british is on the right of the pakistani##1
11. the polish is on the left or right of the mexican##3
12. the mexican is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
13. the pakistani is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
14. the pakistani is on the left or right of the indian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4     |     5     |    6     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | 7up     | soy-milk | fanta    | sprite       | water  |
| Nationality   | australian | indian | pakistani       | british | mexican | polish |

