.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-3::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  pilot, security-guard, paramedic, videographer, firefighter, chef
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, tram, jet-ski, roller, bike, scooter
1. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the pilot##3
2. the firefighter is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the pilot is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
4. the paramedic is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
5. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
6. the videographer is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
7. the security-guard is between the videographer and the paramedic##2
8. the firefighter is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |      3      |     4     |    5     |     6     |
| Job         | videographer | security-guard | paramedic | firefighter | pilot  | chef    |
| Transport   | scooter      | jet-ski  | bike  | tram       | boat | roller |

