.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-4::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, lemonade, water, cola, milk
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, board-games, magic-tricks, photography, hiking, collecting
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the person drinking cola is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person drinking water##1
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 8. the person drinking milk is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person drinking cola##2
 9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5    |       6       |
| Beverage   | coffee   | milk     | cola | iced-tea        | water   | lemonade |
| Hobby      | chess | hiking | magic-tricks  | board-games | collecting | photography       |

