.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-5::.
There 6 different types of food: artichoke, cauliflower, banana, potato, lime, pineapple
There are 6 different nationalities: turkish, egyptian, argentine, pakistani, french, colombian
1. the person eating banana is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating lime##2
2. the colombian is on the left or right of the argentine##3
3. the french is on the left of the person eating lime##1
4. the colombian is the person eating cauliflower##1
5. the argentine is on the far right##1
6. the turkish is the person eating lime##1
7. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
8. the french is on the far left##1
9. the turkish is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |     5     |    6     |
| Food          | pineapple | lime | banana | artichoke | cauliflower | potato   |
| Nationality   | french   | turkish   | egyptian    | pakistani | colombian    | argentine |

