.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-6::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  coach, electrician, musician, doctor, freelancer, analyst
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: water-polo, rugby, sailing, biathlon, basketball, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the coach##3
 2. the coach is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the analyst##2
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the musician##1
 5. the doctor is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
 7. the coach is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 8. the doctor is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 9. the analyst is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the electrician is on the far left##1
11. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |   2    |     3     |     4      |      5       |        6        |
| Job     | electrician        | doctor | analyst | coach  | musician  | freelancer |
| Sport   | sailing | rugby   | water-polo  | surfing | biathlon | basketball          |

