.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-7::.
6 different pets are kept: horse, fish, turtle, pony, dog, bird
The people use 6 different means of transport: roller, trike, helicopter, bike, jet-ski, train
 1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 8. the person driving the roller is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is the owner of the pony##1
10. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the pony and the person driving the trike##2
11. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |    3     |     4      |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | bird | turtle      | pony | dog | fish | horse |
| Transport   | trike  | roller | jet-ski   | train        | helicopter   | bike |

