.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-9::.
There are 6 different nationalities: polish, italian, turkish, nigerian, american, pakistani
6 different pets are kept: mouse, snake, turtle, dog, guinea-pig, chinchilla
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the turkish##1
 2. the turkish is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 3. the nigerian is on the left of the american##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
 5. the owner of the snake is the nigerian##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
 7. the italian is the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the italian is on the right of the american##1
 9. the nigerian is between the american and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
10. the owner of the chinchilla is the pakistani##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the polish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |    5     |     6     |
| Nationality   | polish | pakistani | turkish | nigerian   | american | italian |
| Pet           | turtle    | chinchilla    | guinea-pig   | snake | dog | mouse      |

