 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
 8. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
 9. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
