 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
 6. the person eating radish is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching scientific movies is the person eating radish##1
 8. the person eating potato is between the person watching thriller movies and the person eating pear##2
 9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
10. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1

