 5. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3

